	* MonoDevelop.Core.mdp: Updated.

2005-12-01  Todd Berman  <tberman@off.net>

	* MonoDevelop.Core.AddIns.Setup/SetupService.cs: Make ReadObject
	return null if it encounters an error. This happens with 0 length
	files.

